  	<artifactId>maven-datapower-plugin</artifactId>
  	<packaging>maven-plugin</packaging>
  	<version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
  	<name>Maven DataPower Plugin</name>
  	<description>
This plugin provides goals for:
- Generating DataPower configuration based on predefined templates and specified WSDL files.
- Importing files to a DataPower device.
- Importing a pre-generated configuration to a DataPower device.
  	</description>>
  	<url>http://maven.apache.org</url>
